# 🤖 AI Text Summarizer

A simple AI-powered Text Summarizer built using Python, Streamlit, and OpenAI API.

## 🚀 Features

- Summarizes long text into 3 clear lines
- Uses Large Language Models (LLMs)
- Simple and interactive web interface
- Built with Generative AI concepts

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- OpenAI API
- Prompt Engineering

## 📦 Installation

1. Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/dineshTech-creator/ai-text-summarizer.git

2. Navigate to project folder

cd ai-text-summarizer

3. Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Set your OpenAI API key

On Windows:
setx OPENAI_API_KEY "your_api_key_here"

On Mac/Linux:
export OPENAI_API_KEY="your_api_key_here"

5. Run the app

streamlit run app.py

